.TH "LIGHTNING-INVOICE-CREATE-ZEROCONF" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-invoice-create-zeroconf \- create an invoice for zeroconf channel acceptance
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning invoice-create-zeroconf
.I amount_msat label
.RI [ desc ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Creates a standard BOLT11 invoice via CLN. Intended for use with zeroconf channel partners where the invoice is paid as part of the channel-open flow.
.PP
Output: JSON object from CLN's invoice command including payment_hash, bolt11, expires_at.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-create-offer (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-decode (1)
